ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49677c50991b032511d6dea9eeefe72f877bc22d","tid":2106112,"uid":271303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:00:43.000Z","msg":"日日都跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪就執得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2365000/2368013/88779_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2365000%2F2368013%2F88779_600.png&h=00a87de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://imoney.hket.com/article/2368013?fbclid=IwAR1T0mHWQYN1Tavkbr4Dat8ZpN3DWa-SklQBzdW4sYfzQ-i_CFX9Zgj_-UU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimoney.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2368013%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1T0mHWQYN1Tavkbr4Dat8ZpN3DWa-SklQBzdW4sYfzQ-i_CFX9Zgj_-UU&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=66dd6e92\" target=\"_blank\">http://imoney.hket.com/article/2368013?fbclid=IwAR1T0mHWQYN1Tavkbr4Dat8ZpN3DWa-SklQBzdW4sYfzQ-i_CFX9Zgj_-UU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">陳永堅</span>也指香港方面，現在<span class=\"red\">香港人用煤氣已愈來愈少</span>，「以前一戶有3人，現在一戶只有2.5個人，人口少了，每個家庭簡單了，在家煮食要求又低了，洗澡會在家吃飯未必，好多人出街食，尤其住在納米樓的，<span class=\"red\">基本上沒有廚房</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n他也坦言，<span class=\"red\">煤氣跟電力的競爭很大</span>，「一條煤氣喉來到你家，入到廚房，是否代表你煮食會全用到煤氣？實際上並不如此，如你煲飯會用電飯煲，我相信有99%的香港人也用電飯煲煲飯，你煲湯很多時用電子瓦罉、壓力煲等，你早餐吃的多士也是用多士爐製作，也是用電的；以往用水煲煲水，現在大家也普遍改用電水煲，70年代後也出現了微波爐，其後也有電磁爐的出現，<span class=\"red\">因此電力取了我們很多的市場</span>，電力跟我們有很大競爭。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲連登仔覺得自己醒過煤氣管理層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab217493bf3cc4b7d791b88d23ee4d9cb6ce26b0","tid":2106112,"uid":331838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"正股驚西"},{"pid":"3e5067c346fa32a8c82b5987b7cf1754b975cfa9","tid":2106112,"uid":17134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:48:26.000Z","msg":"50，150，200天線都係向下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e3aef7ef4649808593d6aea70c420608105f12","tid":2106112,"uid":68728,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ab217493bf3cc4b7d791b88d23ee4d9cb6ce26b0","tid":2106112,"uid":331838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"正股驚西"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T14:03:26.000Z","msg":"正股驚西？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n古有匯豐 電盈 中移動 思捷苦主<br />\n今有煤氣 港鐵 領展苦主<br />\n<br />\nHistory repeats itself<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我仲記得當年啲人點吹奏&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n電盈： 穩穩陣陣 收息股 唔會死 仲有科網增長概念 穩中求勝 （好似今日煤氣）<br />\n<br />\n中移用：人人都要用 又有阿爺照 點會有事 （好似今日港鐵）<br />\n<br />\n思捷：啲人話管理層夠勁夠進取 無視主席邢李源不斷減持（好似今日領展）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n痴線 歷史真係倒模一樣 十年又發生多次"},{"pid":"fe8980bf874e6a8c8f3e76917ff3ee71f6718466","tid":2106112,"uid":13101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T14:09:34.000Z","msg":"有2手好撚想放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a082aaf4a20dff6e99f15313468cb1c0b33949","tid":2106112,"uid":174001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12e3aef7ef4649808593d6aea70c420608105f12","tid":2106112,"uid":68728,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ab217493bf3cc4b7d791b88d23ee4d9cb6ce26b0","tid":2106112,"uid":331838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"正股驚西"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T14:03:26.000Z","msg":"正股驚西？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smil